text: Peter Ebinger (10 October 1958 - 24 August 2015) was an Austrian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Austrian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Austria Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vienna
